These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, cola
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, architect
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, romance
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, thai
2 different pets are kept: pony, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the writer is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
4. the spanish is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | cola    |
| Job           | architect | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | musical   |
| Nationality   | thai  | spanish     |
| Pet           | mouse       | pony     |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | ship        |

