.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, traveling
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, classical
2 different pets are kept: turtle, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, taxi
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person drinking cola is the fan of classical##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | cola   |
| Hobby         | traveling | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | epic   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | classical     |
| Pet           | fish        | turtle    |
| Transport     | subway  | taxi    |

