.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, watermelon
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, disaster
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, british
2 different pets are kept: pony, frog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, rugby
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
3. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | watermelon    | cabbage      |
| Hobby         | collecting   | rock-climbing       |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | crime |
| Nationality   | british  | russian    |
| Pet           | pony       | frog   |
| Sport         | rugby   | swimming     |

